{"title_page": "List of proposed state mergers", "text_new": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\n{{For|proposed annexations of non-sovereign territories|List of irredentist claims or disputes}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2015}}\n{{Multiple issues|\n{{more citations needed|date=April 2011}}\n{{original research|date=April 2011}}\n}}\nThis is a '''list of proposed state mergers''', including both current and historical proposals originating from sovereign states or organizations. The entities listed below differ from [[List of active separatist movements|separatist movements]] in that they would form as a merger or union of two or more existing [[Sovereign state|states]], [[Territory (country subdivision)|territories]], [[colony|colonies]] or other regions, becoming either a [[federation]], [[confederation]] or other type of unified [[sovereign state]].\n\n==Historic==\n\n===Until the 15th century===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! scope=\"col\" width=\"130\" | Proposed state\n! scope=\"col\" width=\"150\" | Components\n! scope=\"col\" width=\"70\" | Time period\n! scope=\"col\" width=\"80\" | Successful?\n! scope=\"col\" width=\"620\" | Notes\n|-\n| {{flagicon image|Flag.svg}} [[Union of Hungary and Poland#Angevin Union|Angevin Union]]\n| {{flagicon image|Flag of Hungary (1301-1382, rectangular).svg}} [[Kingdom of Hungary]]<br />{{flagicon image|Alex K Kingdom of Poland-flag.svg}} [[Kingdom of Poland (1025\u20131385)]]\n| 1370\n| {{yes|Yes <br /> (1370\u20131382)}}\n| See [[Union of Hungary and Poland]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon image|Flag.svg}} [[Union of Hungary and Poland#Jagiellonian Union|Jagiellonian Union]]\n| {{flagicon image|Flag of Hungary (15th century, rectangular).svg}} [[Kingdom of Hungary]]<br />{{flagicon image|Alex K Kingdom of Poland-flag.svg}} [[Kingdom of Poland (1385\u20131569)]]\n| 1440\n| {{yes|Yes <br /> (1440\u20131444)}}\n| See [[Union of Hungary and Poland]]\n|}\n\n===Early modern period===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! scope=\"col\" width=\"130\